# Egyland Project Structure

- Entry point: [manage.py](mdc:manage.py) (Django management script)
- Configuration: [egyland/settings.py](mdc:egyland/settings.py) (Django settings)
- URL Configuration: [egyland/urls.py](mdc:egyland/urls.py) (Main URL routing)

## Directory Structure:
- `apps/` - Contains Django applications
  - `core/` - Core functionality
  - `accounts/` - User authentication and profiles
  - `products/` - Product management
  - `dashboard/` - Admin dashboard functionality
  
- `templates/` - HTML templates (pre-designed templates should not be modified)
  - `base/` - Base templates that others extend from
  - `components/` - Reusable template components
  - `core/` - Core application templates
  - `products/` - Product-related templates
  - `dashboard/` - Dashboard templates

- `static/` - Static assets
  - `css/` - Compiled CSS files
  - `scss/` - SCSS source files
  - `js/` - JavaScript files
  - `img/` - Image assets

- `media/` - User-uploaded content

- `config/` - Configuration files

- `logs/` - Application logs

